<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV110">
<l>tūyaṉāyu maṉṟiyuñcu rumpulāvu taṇṭuḻāy</l>
<l>māya.niṉṉai nāyiṉēṉva ṇaṅkivāḻttu mītelām</l>
<l>nīyuniṉku ṟippiṉiṟpo ṟuttunalku vēlainīrp</l>
<l>pāyalōṭu pattarcittam mēyavēlai vaṇṇaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O dark Lord with cool tulasi around which bees wander!</l>
<l>Do forbear in Your inmost thought all this—the worshipping and praising of You,</l>
<l rend="indent">By me, a dog, being purified and without [being so]—</l>
<l>And show favour! O ocean-hued [Lord] who dwell in the thoughts</l>
<l>Of the devotees, as well as [on] the bedding on the ocean water!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
